WEBVTT

01:35.540 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 1]

02:33.030 --> 02:33.850
Why's someone lying there?

02:33.870 --> 02:34.470
What's going on?

02:34.470 --> 02:37.500
[Seventh day of the tenth month]

02:43.450 --> 02:44.130
Someone's dead!

02:44.650 --> 02:45.460
Someone's dead!

02:51.220 --> 02:53.660
[The Well-Woven House]

02:56.260 --> 02:57.100
Did you hear?

02:57.360 --> 02:58.060
Last night,

02:58.120 --> 02:59.290
they found another body.

02:59.480 --> 03:00.380
So scary!

03:00.380 --> 03:02.540
[Fourteenth day of the tenth month]

03:04.610 --> 03:05.450
Again, his heart

03:05.630 --> 03:06.680
was ripped out.

03:07.840 --> 03:10.220
I heard a high-rank demon's here.

03:10.590 --> 03:11.450
So we can't stay

03:11.590 --> 03:12.820
in Luo'an anymore.

03:12.960 --> 03:14.170
Now the whole town's in panic.

03:14.630 --> 03:15.890
That demon will surely

03:15.910 --> 03:16.820
keep killing and taking hearts.

03:17.430 --> 03:19.060
Who knows who'll be next?

03:19.230 --> 03:20.660
[Twenty-first day of the tenth month]
How terrifying!

03:20.840 --> 03:22.260
To keep their wedding going,

03:22.520 --> 03:23.570
the Wei family specially hired

03:23.590 --> 03:24.730
a demon hunter from the Shilin Sect.

03:25.310 --> 03:26.660
- This isn't just any demon hunter, - Good.

03:27.000 --> 03:28.100
- That's it! - but someone with a flower on his forehead!

03:28.310 --> 03:28.780
Good.

03:36.870 --> 03:38.060
Miss, you are...?

03:38.570 --> 03:40.780
I'm the Wei family's bride-to-be's...

03:49.710 --> 03:50.610
cousin.

03:51.150 --> 03:51.820
My name's Yu Wei.

03:53.680 --> 03:54.570
Please, follow me.

04:01.500 --> 04:03.080
[Wei Qing, head of the Wei family]

04:03.080 --> 04:03.660
Here, Shengwei.

04:06.420 --> 04:08.590
[Yu Shengwei, daughter of the Yu family]

04:08.590 --> 04:09.500
Master Wei.

04:12.180 --> 04:13.240
[Luo Wei, steward of the Wei mansion]

04:13.240 --> 04:14.730
The wedding dress will be done in two days.

04:15.400 --> 04:17.380
I'll deliver it to the Yu mansion myself.

04:18.120 --> 04:20.170
Guess we should go pray at the Dragon Deity Temple.

04:20.920 --> 04:22.750
May we stay deeply in love,

04:22.750 --> 04:23.700
and grow old together.

04:23.870 --> 04:24.540
What do you think?

04:26.270 --> 04:26.980
Come on, Wei Qing.

04:31.750 --> 04:33.460
The Dragon Deity doesn't handle that stuff.

04:33.460 --> 04:34.430
[Liu Weixue, Wei Qing's cousin]

04:34.430 --> 04:35.170
Master Wei.

04:38.120 --> 04:39.460
Miss Yu's cousin has arrived.

04:47.630 --> 04:48.460
You are...?

04:50.240 --> 04:51.220
Shengwei.

04:52.600 --> 04:54.170
I know it's been a while,

04:54.480 --> 04:55.850
but you really don't recognize me?

04:56.750 --> 04:57.900
I'm your cousin,

04:58.830 --> 04:59.580
Yu Wei.

05:04.880 --> 05:05.730
Oh, I remember now.

05:07.750 --> 05:08.570
You're Yu Wei.

05:14.780 --> 05:19.140
[Twenty-fourth day of the tenth month]

06:10.440 --> 06:11.340
I've got a hostage now!

06:12.160 --> 06:13.620
Dare you chase me anymore?

06:19.720 --> 06:20.500
Ow, that hurts!

06:38.280 --> 06:39.170
What's your problem?

06:46.750 --> 06:47.500
What kind of weirdo are you?

06:47.750 --> 06:48.700
Why'd you hang me up?

06:48.950 --> 06:49.620
Untie me, now!

06:50.080 --> 06:51.460
You demon hunters are something else.

06:52.000 --> 06:53.060
Go after that greater fox demon

06:53.080 --> 06:54.220
that's been killing and stealing hearts.

06:54.830 --> 06:55.620
Why come after me,

06:55.920 --> 06:57.210
an innocent little weasel?

06:57.470 --> 06:58.060
Save it.

06:58.470 --> 06:58.900
Get in!

06:59.600 --> 07:01.580
No, please!

07:15.720 --> 07:16.700
Thank you, kind sir,

07:16.750 --> 07:17.960
for saving my life a second time.

07:18.240 --> 07:19.340
No problem, Miss Yu.

07:20.830 --> 07:21.610
Second time?

07:28.950 --> 07:30.100
Master Wei's arranged

07:30.160 --> 07:30.940
a dinner banquet

07:31.160 --> 07:32.220
to thank you, Master.

07:34.190 --> 07:35.100
Please rest here for now.

07:36.310 --> 07:36.810
Thanks.

07:43.500 --> 07:46.820
[Wu Shiguang]

07:51.310 --> 07:51.940
So?

07:52.260 --> 07:53.440
[You Chi, low-rank weasel demon]
Did I nail my act?

07:53.510 --> 07:54.290
All thanks

07:54.390 --> 07:55.660
to my majestic black smoke.

07:55.870 --> 07:57.020
Absolutely brilliant!

08:00.510 --> 08:01.250
Half a month ago,

08:02.040 --> 08:03.540
a broken-tail fox attacked Miss Yu.

08:04.040 --> 08:05.410
It must be linked to the heart-stealing one.

08:07.120 --> 08:07.730
Otherwise,

08:08.240 --> 08:10.220
those arrogant demon hunters from the Shilin Sect

08:10.830 --> 08:11.730
wouldn't have been guards

08:11.730 --> 08:13.050
for an ordinary family.

08:15.800 --> 08:16.230
You Chi!

08:18.720 --> 08:19.140
Come in!

08:44.960 --> 08:46.180
Yu told me

08:46.670 --> 08:47.580
how you were kind enough

08:47.750 --> 08:49.060
to save her half a month ago.

08:49.510 --> 08:51.150
She could've died.

08:52.320 --> 08:53.130
Thank you, Master.

08:54.390 --> 08:55.130
It was nothing.

09:00.000 --> 09:00.890
But that time,

09:01.920 --> 09:02.940
it was really dangerous.

09:03.980 --> 09:05.840
[Half a month ago]

09:05.840 --> 09:06.370
Help!

09:06.740 --> 09:07.920
[Seventh day of the tenth month]

09:07.920 --> 09:08.500
Help!

09:09.670 --> 09:10.260
Help!

09:27.670 --> 09:28.420
Eight tails...

09:29.550 --> 09:30.610
A broken-tail fox!

09:32.510 --> 09:33.010
Run!

09:43.200 --> 09:44.490
That fox demon moves without a trace.

09:45.910 --> 09:46.650
Really terrifying.

09:51.390 --> 09:52.010
Shengwei,

09:52.870 --> 09:54.530
have your favorite chestnut cake.

09:55.000 --> 09:55.700
It may comfort you.

10:01.270 --> 10:02.770
Master Wu, you're truly amazing.

10:03.270 --> 10:04.770
If you hadn't chased that fox demon off,

10:05.670 --> 10:06.300
my cousin's heart

10:06.790 --> 10:08.490
would've been ripped out too.

10:09.000 --> 10:10.060
I didn't exactly chase it off.

10:10.720 --> 10:11.820
And that day marked

10:11.910 --> 10:12.820
the first murder

10:13.000 --> 10:14.340
in this whole heart-stealing case.

10:14.910 --> 10:15.770
That broken-tail fox

10:16.200 --> 10:17.250
must be the culprit.

10:18.390 --> 10:19.770
It might've been hiding in this mansion,

10:20.440 --> 10:21.460
so it will try again

10:22.240 --> 10:23.340
to harm Miss Yu.

10:27.120 --> 10:27.850
Master Wu,

10:28.270 --> 10:29.610
are you serious?

10:32.720 --> 10:35.060
The air above this estate is thick with demonic energy.

10:35.630 --> 10:37.060
I fear a high-rank demon has taken root here.

10:38.550 --> 10:39.420
Master Wei,

10:39.670 --> 10:40.820
if you're willing to hire me as a house guard,

10:41.440 --> 10:43.370
I can definitely protect Miss Yu.

10:44.630 --> 10:45.730
That's great!

10:47.240 --> 10:49.530
Although Master Wu is just a wandering hunter

10:49.720 --> 10:51.940
with no real background,

10:52.320 --> 10:53.180
although

10:53.390 --> 10:54.530
he couldn't actually defeat

10:54.550 --> 10:55.460
the fox demon last time,

10:56.120 --> 10:56.980
although

10:57.510 --> 10:59.250
he probably still doesn't know

10:59.360 --> 11:01.010
where the fox demon is

11:01.320 --> 11:02.420
or how to guard against it,

11:04.600 --> 11:05.650
although no one knows

11:06.000 --> 11:07.940
if he could win if it does show up...

11:09.000 --> 11:09.730
one thing's sure...

11:12.750 --> 11:14.490
he's so handsome,

11:15.000 --> 11:16.770
with such a great build.

11:18.120 --> 11:19.420
Having him stay

11:19.510 --> 11:21.770
by my cousin's side,

11:22.440 --> 11:25.180
Shengwei will surely be "safe."

11:29.150 --> 11:30.100
Yeah, sure thing!

11:37.840 --> 11:38.730
Master Wu,

11:39.360 --> 11:40.460
see you later!

11:44.080 --> 11:45.250
I thought it was a sure thing,

11:46.360 --> 11:47.730
but Wei Qing's got such a small mind!

11:49.440 --> 11:50.100
So petty.

11:50.840 --> 11:51.610
The one

11:51.670 --> 11:52.570
who really wants us gone

11:53.270 --> 11:54.180
isn't Wei Qing,

11:56.080 --> 11:57.100
but this cousin of hers.

12:21.530 --> 12:22.030
Who's there?

12:38.720 --> 12:39.300
Rucui.

12:40.200 --> 12:41.010
Is it time yet?

12:44.750 --> 12:45.300
Rucui?

12:56.750 --> 12:57.250
Quiet.

13:20.720 --> 13:21.770
Follow my lead.

14:06.160 --> 14:06.530
Hey,

14:07.230 --> 14:07.820
are we sure

14:07.840 --> 14:08.660
this isn't dangerous?

14:09.000 --> 14:11.060
The heart thefts started on Oct 7th.

14:11.760 --> 14:13.370
Every seven days, someone dies.

14:14.200 --> 14:14.810
Today,

14:15.200 --> 14:17.230
the fox demon should strike again.

14:18.120 --> 14:19.940
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

14:20.830 --> 14:22.330
If you want to catch the heart-stealing demon

14:22.350 --> 14:23.620
and claim the bounty from the Shilin Sect,

14:24.080 --> 14:25.420
then shut up, okay?

14:26.710 --> 14:28.580
So the fox demon wanted to kill Miss Yu that day,

14:28.600 --> 14:29.490
but failed,

14:30.030 --> 14:31.490
so it killed someone else instead.

14:31.960 --> 14:33.220
Then every seven days after,

14:33.350 --> 14:34.260
it kills one person on schedule.

14:34.400 --> 14:35.170
Yeah, that's it!

14:37.110 --> 14:38.690
I'm just too smart.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.650
Are you even listening to me?

14:52.640 --> 14:53.290
Yeah.

15:08.900 --> 15:11.820
[Twenty-eighth day of the tenth month, auspicious for weddings]

15:18.640 --> 15:20.110
Congratulations!

15:20.390 --> 15:21.400
[The Well-Woven House]
Congrats!

15:21.400 --> 15:21.920
Please, come in!

15:21.950 --> 15:22.590
Come on in!

15:23.850 --> 15:24.840
Just put it over there.

15:24.840 --> 15:25.820
Right this way!

15:25.820 --> 15:27.030
Come, this way please!

15:29.330 --> 15:30.260
What a perfect day!

15:31.200 --> 15:31.770
Congrats!

15:33.400 --> 15:35.200
Come on, right inside!

15:42.060 --> 15:44.030
[Ji Ling]
The nine-tailed fox's magic is right in my hand.

15:49.500 --> 15:51.380
[Li Jie]

15:51.390 --> 15:51.940
Impressive.

15:52.440 --> 15:52.850
Let's go!

15:55.170 --> 15:55.790
Alright!

15:55.790 --> 15:56.440
[The Well-Woven House]

15:56.440 --> 15:57.040
Please, come in!

15:57.040 --> 15:58.150
- Come on in! - This way, please!

16:03.820 --> 16:04.940
- No need for formalities. - Congratulations!

16:05.480 --> 16:06.080
Congratulations!

16:06.440 --> 16:08.030
- Congrats! - Right this way!

16:08.030 --> 16:08.700
Gentlemen,

16:09.240 --> 16:10.250
it's crowded and busy inside.

16:10.600 --> 16:11.700
Please leave your names

16:11.870 --> 16:13.060
and your wedding gifts,

16:13.870 --> 16:15.060
so I can record them properly.

16:16.630 --> 16:17.490
Well, the gifts...

16:18.150 --> 16:19.370
The gifts...

16:19.910 --> 16:20.460
Li Jie.

16:23.440 --> 16:24.060
What are you looking at me for?

16:27.000 --> 16:27.610
Congratulations.

16:33.600 --> 16:34.700
All these human customs

16:35.120 --> 16:36.100
are such a hassle.

16:37.960 --> 16:38.770
This door's flimsy.

16:39.670 --> 16:40.980
I could smash it with one swing.

16:44.270 --> 16:44.730
Rude.

16:48.500 --> 16:50.320
[The Well-Woven House]

16:50.320 --> 16:51.460
Oh, Master Qi!

16:52.200 --> 16:54.130
Your presence honors our humble home!

16:57.360 --> 16:58.100
Madame Zhao,

16:58.100 --> 16:58.800
you've arrived!

16:59.530 --> 17:00.830
Come in, please!

18:17.200 --> 18:18.380
You're not Miss Yu.

18:19.270 --> 18:20.140
Miss Yu

18:20.790 --> 18:22.730
doesn't have a vixen face like that.

18:23.400 --> 18:24.730
And you're not Master Wei.

18:25.680 --> 18:26.570
Master Wei

18:27.350 --> 18:29.050
wouldn't hold a knife to me.

18:34.550 --> 18:35.460
You're so eager?

18:38.400 --> 18:39.330
They say

18:40.350 --> 18:42.730
the first night together is priceless.

18:43.000 --> 18:44.140
How could I not be eager?

18:46.110 --> 18:47.700
Since we're now wed,

18:48.680 --> 18:49.380
then...

18:50.270 --> 18:52.220
we should be open with each other!

18:57.790 --> 18:58.900
I never thought

18:59.790 --> 19:01.660
my husband would have two faces.

19:03.790 --> 19:04.490
Too bad

19:05.510 --> 19:07.460
one woman shouldn't serve two husbands.

19:08.830 --> 19:09.700
That makes sense.

19:11.440 --> 19:12.420
So, how about

19:13.480 --> 19:14.730
you let me down first?

19:15.680 --> 19:16.900
Well then, sir,

19:18.240 --> 19:19.180
you'll have to

19:19.200 --> 19:21.250
take that dagger away from me first.

19:33.960 --> 19:34.700
Trying to leave?

20:13.030 --> 20:14.420
Such a beautiful vase,

20:15.160 --> 20:16.330
and you have no taste for elegance.

20:16.960 --> 20:18.330
Someone as beautiful as me,

20:18.680 --> 20:19.860
and you have no taste either.

20:20.440 --> 20:22.220
Tonight, I'm divorcing you!

20:28.510 --> 20:29.090
So?

20:32.320 --> 20:32.900
Pretty clever.

20:35.560 --> 20:37.010
Isn't that Steward Luo of this family?

20:37.680 --> 20:38.770
Why is she sneaking around

20:38.920 --> 20:39.900
in her own house?

20:40.630 --> 20:41.290
Something's off.

20:42.600 --> 20:43.290
Let's check it out!

22:19.030 --> 22:19.980
Who are you?

22:21.280 --> 22:22.220
Her accomplices?

22:35.400 --> 22:36.290
What's going on?

22:42.960 --> 22:43.980
Why are you stopping me?

22:44.790 --> 22:45.980
You reek of demonic energy.

22:46.680 --> 22:47.450
You're a fox demon!

22:48.160 --> 22:50.010
She's that heart-eating demon.

22:53.310 --> 22:54.770
Heaven really is fair.

22:55.510 --> 22:57.290
It gives you such a handsome face,

22:57.680 --> 22:59.490
but no brains to go with it.

23:14.880 --> 23:15.580
Groom,

23:16.680 --> 23:18.290
why the sudden change of your face?

23:19.630 --> 23:20.420
Your opponent

23:21.070 --> 23:21.890
is me.

24:24.510 --> 24:25.380
You have no sacred power?

24:26.070 --> 24:26.940
Does that

24:27.280 --> 24:28.380
stop me from fighting you?

25:30.910 --> 25:32.060
Who exactly are you guys?

25:33.110 --> 25:33.850
I'll ask you

25:34.030 --> 25:35.500
the same question.

25:37.110 --> 25:38.530
I'm the demon hunter Wu Shiguang.

25:40.080 --> 25:40.850
Since when do demon hunters

25:40.870 --> 25:42.310
have to worry about so much,

25:42.760 --> 25:43.780
even playing the groom?

25:44.160 --> 25:45.140
I'm pretending to be the groom

25:46.110 --> 25:47.140
for one reason only...

25:49.080 --> 25:49.770
to catch a demon.

25:54.030 --> 25:54.700
What a coincidence.

25:55.280 --> 25:56.410
We're demon hunters too.

25:56.790 --> 25:57.890
We're also here to catch demons.

25:58.990 --> 26:00.060
But unlike you back-alley,

26:00.110 --> 26:01.410
rogue demon hunters,

26:01.600 --> 26:03.940
we're official demon hunters from the Shilin Sect,

26:04.520 --> 26:05.410
sent here

26:05.430 --> 26:07.060
to investigate the heart-stealing case.

26:07.550 --> 26:08.580
This is the Shilin Sect's

26:08.600 --> 26:09.300
demon hunter commander,

26:09.400 --> 26:10.060
Li Jie.

26:13.720 --> 26:14.330
Stunned now?

26:37.160 --> 26:38.300
An ice-wielding demon.

26:39.520 --> 26:40.180
Sure enough,

26:40.910 --> 26:42.210
you're the one we're after!

26:42.870 --> 26:44.580
What grudge do we have?

26:44.910 --> 26:46.140
I don't even know you.

26:48.430 --> 26:49.140
Trying to run?

27:23.400 --> 27:24.140
It's you!

27:30.440 --> 27:31.250
Sir,

27:32.550 --> 27:33.420
save me...

27:40.200 --> 27:40.980
Let... let her go!

27:42.310 --> 27:43.090
Sir,

27:43.750 --> 27:44.980
what's going on?

27:47.160 --> 27:47.700
Who's there?

27:56.920 --> 27:57.530
Still trying to flee?

28:40.680 --> 28:42.010
Thank you, sir, for saving me.

28:44.790 --> 28:45.380
Well...

28:46.160 --> 28:47.140
You're thanking the wrong person.

28:47.440 --> 28:48.380
The groom saved you.

28:48.550 --> 28:49.220
Thank him instead!

28:54.420 --> 28:55.890
Thank you, kind sir.

28:56.750 --> 28:57.420
You're welcome!

28:58.790 --> 28:59.980
What are those red threads

29:00.000 --> 29:00.730
made of?

29:04.680 --> 29:05.250
I guess

29:05.920 --> 29:06.420
it's blood.

29:08.240 --> 29:09.090
Submit now,

29:09.750 --> 29:10.860
or die trying?

29:12.070 --> 29:12.660
It's your choice.

29:14.110 --> 29:15.810
Do I look like I'm struggling?

29:16.880 --> 29:17.980
I'm a demon hunter too,

29:18.510 --> 29:19.620
here to catch demons.

29:20.110 --> 29:21.050
What crime have I committed?

29:21.160 --> 29:21.770
Fine.

29:23.240 --> 29:24.620
Now the whole room's full of demon hunters,

29:24.640 --> 29:25.140
isn't it?

29:26.720 --> 29:27.980
Don't count me in.

29:29.310 --> 29:30.670
I'm no demon hunter.

29:31.030 --> 29:32.660
I'm a respectable woman.

29:33.510 --> 29:34.180
Don't bother denying it!

29:34.510 --> 29:35.460
We traced the demonic energy

29:35.480 --> 29:36.250
right here.

29:36.590 --> 29:38.050
You're the nine-tailed fox stealing hearts!

29:45.070 --> 29:45.980
How terrifying!

29:46.960 --> 29:47.530
Just now,

29:48.240 --> 29:49.900
was she trying to rip out my heart?

29:51.750 --> 29:52.420
Me?

29:53.110 --> 29:54.330
A heart-eating demon?

29:55.640 --> 29:57.050
Are you joking,

29:57.830 --> 29:58.900
or serious?

29:59.100 --> 30:00.050
- I... - Who has time

30:00.070 --> 30:01.220
to joke with a fox demon like you?

30:03.400 --> 30:05.530
You're the sect's demon hunter commander.

30:07.030 --> 30:07.860
And you?

30:08.960 --> 30:10.290
What's your identity?

30:12.480 --> 30:13.140
Me?

30:20.160 --> 30:20.770
Sir!

30:21.590 --> 30:22.420
What should I call you?

30:22.670 --> 30:23.530
My name is Ji Ling.

30:23.720 --> 30:24.690
Ji means "life's a journey,"

30:24.750 --> 30:25.530
and Ling means "hearts that beat as one."

30:25.830 --> 30:26.420
Stay here,

30:26.480 --> 30:27.090
and don't run off, okay?

30:29.200 --> 30:29.900
Sir!

30:30.590 --> 30:32.220
Please don't leave me alone!

30:32.960 --> 30:34.570
This female demon is really terrifying!

30:35.720 --> 30:36.490
I'm so scared!

30:36.920 --> 30:37.730
So scary!

30:38.830 --> 30:39.700
So scary...

30:45.110 --> 30:45.700
You demon!

31:11.100 --> 31:13.580
[Li Mao, wedding guest of the Wei family]

31:17.700 --> 31:19.780
[Tao Xi, Li Mao's wife]

31:37.000 --> 31:38.090
Weimiao Pavilion...

31:48.440 --> 31:48.860
Blood...

32:19.200 --> 32:19.900
It's frost.

32:25.350 --> 32:26.140
It's not even winter yet.

32:27.070 --> 32:28.050
Why is there all this frost?

32:30.510 --> 32:31.250
It's demon magic.

32:42.360 --> 32:43.740
Those prayer beads are amazing.

32:44.640 --> 32:45.490
What's their story?

32:51.430 --> 32:52.010
Don't touch them.

32:55.190 --> 32:55.740
Keep them there.

32:56.750 --> 32:58.220
You're so thoughtful.

32:58.590 --> 32:59.330
Whatever you say.

33:00.350 --> 33:01.380
And you're so clever.

33:01.880 --> 33:03.250
Thanks to you tipping me off,

33:04.000 --> 33:05.380
I was able to prepare.

33:08.790 --> 33:09.420
Wangyan,

33:10.590 --> 33:11.700
the groom's a fake.

33:12.590 --> 33:13.940
He's here to catch fox demons.

33:14.880 --> 33:16.090
Be careful.

33:17.240 --> 33:18.360
Don't let him

33:19.240 --> 33:20.450
make it real,

33:20.590 --> 33:21.810
or turn the tables on you.

33:23.720 --> 33:25.290
I thought we'd guarded against one,

33:25.510 --> 33:26.570
and now two more show up.

33:27.960 --> 33:29.090
That Ji Ling guy

33:30.550 --> 33:32.810
and his long-blade friend

33:33.590 --> 33:34.900
won't be easy either.

33:37.200 --> 33:38.770
But the one really hard to shake

33:39.310 --> 33:40.860
is that guy who won't let me go,

33:40.960 --> 33:42.090
Wu Shiguang.

33:43.310 --> 33:44.090
Oh yeah?

33:46.790 --> 33:47.940
I don't believe it.

33:49.110 --> 33:50.050
Wangyan,

33:51.590 --> 33:52.700
want to make a bet?

35:42.070 --> 35:42.980
Broken-tail fox,

35:44.360 --> 35:45.170
it really is you.

36:35.510 --> 36:36.340
Miss Yu?

36:39.800 --> 36:40.930
I asked you to gather some intel.

36:41.710 --> 36:42.610
Did you get it all?

36:42.960 --> 36:43.740
Of course!

36:44.320 --> 36:46.300
There are 952 weasels in Luo'an City.

36:46.550 --> 36:47.340
From street gossip

36:47.480 --> 36:48.300
to corner rumors,

36:48.550 --> 36:49.300
they know everything.

36:49.760 --> 36:50.920
Let's start with the bride,

36:50.920 --> 36:51.690
Miss Yu.

36:51.920 --> 36:53.060
She's Luo'an's

36:53.110 --> 36:54.160
famous embroiderer,

36:54.400 --> 36:55.170
especially skilled

36:55.760 --> 36:56.780
at stitching birds and beasts.

37:00.070 --> 37:00.940
Now, Luo Wei.

37:01.400 --> 37:02.940
This woman's something else.

37:03.670 --> 37:04.380
A month ago,

37:04.590 --> 37:06.170
the Wei family's business faced a crisis,

37:06.320 --> 37:07.010
almost went bankrupt.

37:07.630 --> 37:09.170
Then Luo Wei appeared out of nowhere

37:09.360 --> 37:10.260
and turned things around.

37:11.070 --> 37:12.160
After that, she joined the Wei mansion

37:12.230 --> 37:13.070
and became the steward.

37:13.360 --> 37:14.050
Everyone in the house

37:14.190 --> 37:15.340
fears and respects her.

37:15.760 --> 37:16.650
And gossip says

37:17.000 --> 37:18.050
she's got a thing for Wei Qing.

37:18.360 --> 37:18.940
So,

37:19.230 --> 37:20.420
she really dislikes Miss Yu.

37:26.400 --> 37:27.460
As for Liu Weixue,

37:27.880 --> 37:29.420
he's Wei Qing's distant cousin.

37:30.150 --> 37:31.380
The Liu family's been generals for generations.

37:31.670 --> 37:32.530
But despite all his skill,

37:32.670 --> 37:34.130
Liu Weixue refuses

37:34.230 --> 37:35.530
to go to war.

37:36.200 --> 37:37.180
- Half a month ago, - Go...

37:37.270 --> 37:39.020
he fled an arranged marriage and came here.

37:39.230 --> 37:40.340
- Bring the wine! - Word on the street is

37:40.600 --> 37:41.940
he might be interested in Luo Wei.

37:42.190 --> 37:43.390
Quick, bring the medicine wine!

37:44.280 --> 37:45.130
What's all this?

37:46.230 --> 37:47.820
So lively late at night?

37:48.360 --> 37:49.130
And Yu Wei

37:49.480 --> 37:50.570
grew up in the countryside,

37:50.840 --> 37:51.690
not from around here.

37:52.190 --> 37:53.010
Their families

37:53.440 --> 37:54.300
rarely interact.

37:55.000 --> 37:56.420
So her showing up for the feast

37:57.360 --> 37:58.420
is pretty strange.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.300
Oh, quite a crowd here.

38:07.920 --> 38:08.740
Miss Yu Wei!

38:09.670 --> 38:10.900
Weren't you supposed to stay in your room?

38:11.150 --> 38:12.380
Why'd you come out?

38:12.840 --> 38:13.940
It's so dangerous!

38:16.550 --> 38:18.260
Since you called her a demon,

38:19.070 --> 38:20.110
how could I stay

38:20.110 --> 38:21.490
in the same room with her?

38:22.710 --> 38:23.490
Plus,

38:24.280 --> 38:26.050
she totally wrecked my clothes.

38:26.670 --> 38:28.170
So I came here

38:28.800 --> 38:29.900
to change into new ones.

38:32.400 --> 38:33.820
So, sir,

38:35.360 --> 38:36.340
do I look good?

38:38.800 --> 38:40.210
Yeah... good.

38:42.550 --> 38:43.210
What's wrong?

38:44.550 --> 38:46.170
Where's the bride I tied up?

38:47.320 --> 38:48.130
Darling,

38:49.230 --> 38:50.570
are you looking for me?

38:59.840 --> 39:01.340
I followed the broken-tail fox here.

39:02.150 --> 39:03.610
But the moment I entered this room,

39:04.440 --> 39:05.300
it vanished.

39:07.110 --> 39:08.170
What do you mean?

39:09.590 --> 39:10.530
I mean,

39:11.670 --> 39:12.860
among all of you here,

39:14.480 --> 39:15.300
one of you

39:16.360 --> 39:18.420
is the heart-stealing killer I'm after,

39:20.190 --> 39:21.610
the broken-tail fox.

39:29.060 --> 39:34.070
[The runaway fox's hiding in the Wei mansion]

39:34.070 --> 39:34.860
Wu Wangyan,

39:35.630 --> 39:37.170
proceed to Luo'an at once

39:38.000 --> 39:39.380
and bring Xiaowei back.

39:41.150 --> 39:41.820
Understood.

39:43.880 --> 39:44.570
What about me?

39:45.280 --> 39:46.210
My mission

39:46.440 --> 39:47.610
is still to assist her?

39:48.440 --> 39:49.260
Your mission

39:49.920 --> 39:51.130
is to get close

39:51.400 --> 39:53.010
to a young man named Ji Ling.

39:53.880 --> 39:55.490
He is your fated one.

39:56.000 --> 39:57.650
Fated one?

40:00.070 --> 40:00.690
Wangyan,

40:01.360 --> 40:02.210
what does this mean?

40:06.840 --> 40:07.420
You hear that?

40:08.110 --> 40:09.010
All five of you

40:09.760 --> 40:10.530
are suspects!

40:11.320 --> 40:12.210
And you two

40:13.760 --> 40:14.610
are no simple cases either.

40:18.840 --> 40:20.780
Bai Ze has brought news

40:20.920 --> 40:22.210
of the nine-tailed fox, Xiaowei.

40:22.210 --> 40:23.280
[Shilin Sect, Scale Cave]

40:23.280 --> 40:24.980
Right now, she's hiding in the Wei mansion

40:25.440 --> 40:26.340
in Luo'an.

40:28.590 --> 40:29.300
Li Jie,

40:30.320 --> 40:32.090
it's time to bring her back.

40:33.480 --> 40:34.090
Understood.

41:40.500 --> 41:41.660
♪It's your light♪

41:41.860 --> 41:43.740
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

41:43.900 --> 41:47.020
♪That set the night alight♪

41:47.380 --> 41:53.900
♪And lead me through the fight♪

41:55.660 --> 41:57.540
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

41:57.980 --> 42:02.420
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

42:03.220 --> 42:04.900
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

42:05.060 --> 42:10.460
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

42:11.220 --> 42:16.620
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

42:18.940 --> 42:24.980
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

42:25.940 --> 42:28.100
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

42:28.380 --> 42:33.220
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

42:33.580 --> 42:35.900
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

42:36.100 --> 42:41.180
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

42:41.420 --> 42:43.420
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

42:43.700 --> 42:48.060
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

42:49.060 --> 42:56.020
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

43:12.580 --> 43:15.540
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

43:16.620 --> 43:20.020
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

43:20.820 --> 43:23.340
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

43:23.580 --> 43:26.660
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

43:27.060 --> 43:29.380
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

43:29.900 --> 43:34.300
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

43:34.540 --> 43:36.700
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

43:37.100 --> 43:42.060
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

43:42.300 --> 43:43.460
♪It's your light♪

43:43.660 --> 43:45.500
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

43:45.700 --> 43:48.820
♪That set the night alight♪

43:49.580 --> 43:59.020
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
